The Prelate of Methodist Church Nigeria, His Eminence Samuel Kanu, was yesterday, kidnapped along the Enugu-Port Harcourt Expressway, in Umunneochi Local Government Area of Abia. He was kidnapped by gunmen alongside Rt. Rev. Dennis Mark, the Methodist Bishop of Owerri and the Prelateâ€™s Chaplain. NAN sources said the clergymen were kidnapped in the afternoon while they were on their way from a programme in the council area. The Police Public Relations Officer in Abia, SP Geoffrey Ogbonna, confirmed the incident.